# No Fake UI

Every visible control must do real work or clearly explain why it is unavailable.

Do not create fake sources, fake set thumbnails, fake uploads, fake preview/program buttons, or fake diagnostics.

For foundation work, the UI must show:

- Active source.
- Active set.
- Source state.
- FPS or runtime status.
- Last runtime issue.

If a button is added, wire it to the actual runtime behavior in the same patch.
